<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #262626;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: #262626;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0095f6;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #8e8e8e;
            border-top: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
        }

        .note {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #8e8e8e;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .link-text {
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #00376b;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Photogram</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
            <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Photogram account. Click the button below to choose
                a new one:</p>

            <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="btn">Reset Password</a>

            <p>If you didn't ask to reset your password, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

            <p class="note">If the button above doesn't work, copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
            <p class="link-text">
                <%= resetLink %>
            </p>

            <p class="note">Request received at: <%= time %>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 Photogram from Hamzah. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>